title: Barstool Pick Em 2017 Week 1
description:
The Barstool Pick Em is officially back. The guys talk about getting back into action this fall. All the big games this weekend including Michigan/Florida, Bama/FSU, and OSU/Indiana. Rico Bosco makes his triumphant return to the show for his locks of the week and must watch Movie Pick + an update on Rico Rider nation!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
